data.description: Enjoy country living with gorgeous views on 1.75 Acres! 3,010 SF daylight ranch with 3 Bedrooms + Office + Family Room, 2 Full Bathrooms & 2 Half-Baths. Builder's custom home with solid 2' x 6' construction. Inviting Living Room with walls of windows to capture the serene setting. Spacious Kitchen with chef's desk and eating nook is just perfect for hosting large gatherings. Family Room with cozy brick fireplace and slider to deck. Primary Suite retreat includes walk-in closet and door to private deck with built-in seating. Mudroom with half bath just off the oversized 827 SF 3-Car Garage with built-in cabinetry and workbench. Updates include: New carpet and interior paint, Newer exterior paint (2020), Newer Lifetime 50-year roof (2019), Newer AC (2018). Storage galore. Incredible!
